description:
This is a 8 minute workout called '15 Most Effective Bodyweight Leg Exercises.' from the channel Strength Side.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Strength/Calisthenics.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Progression Quest and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Advanced.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: Whether you like calisthenics, train at home, or enjoy bodyweight strength you can grow strong power legs if you use the right exercises. This is a complete guide to getting the most out of your bodyweight leg training. Develop legs that are aesthetic and functional with these exercises...
